This paper deals with topological analysis and persistence barcodes, which are commonly used in computational geometry (cs.CG) and topological data analysis (cs.SI). The method proposed in the paper involves comparing persistence barcodes, which is also relevant to the sub-category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper involves measuring entropy, which is a concept commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and data mining (cs.DM).
